    "Therefore, the model is considered to be the best fit based on both absolute and comparative fit indexes.The Table 3 below displays the summary results of the model goodness-of-fit test for the employee engagement construct.",
    "Organizational performance constructThe results of the assessment of construct validity and reliability revealed that all the items used to measure concepts are suitable.",
